title: Horrible - DO NOT BUY
review: Had several problems with this product - the rose flavoring was overpowering (could smell it from opening) and artificial tasting. Like how splenda/stevia dominates in a product.Also, mine arrived rancid - just plain awful. However, customer service was great about taking care of the expired product.Just a bad combo of problems. Not meant to be.
